            <title>[LU-18935] Lustre nodemap ranges do not work with KFI</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18935</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre nodemap ranges do not work with KFI as shown below&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;root@mchstor2n02 ~&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;# lctl nodemap_add_range --name alps --range &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1-131071&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;@kfi&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;root@mchstor2n02 ~&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;# lctl get_param nodemap.alps.ranges&lt;br/&gt;
nodemap.alps.ranges=&lt;br/&gt;
[&lt;/p&gt;
{ id: 8, start_nid: 1@kfi, end_nid: 1@kfi }
&lt;p&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;
{ id: 7, start_nid: 0@kfi, end_nid: 0@kfi }
&lt;p&gt;]&lt;/p&gt;</description>
